                     <interp inst="t18291029-160-person1284" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lived near the prosecutor. I saw the prisoner go into the house with the coals, and come out with a brown cotton umbrella; he took it away with him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18291029-160-person1285">
                  JOHN 
                  MARTIN BALL
               <interp inst="t18291029-160-person1285" type="surname" value="MARTIN BALL"></interp>
