                     <interp inst="t18291029-160-person1285" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was going across Spital-square - I saw two women had hold of the prisoner; he got from them, and I took him to the watch-house.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never had the umbrella, nor saw one there.</p>
